Zoxenpher has an image viewer. You can open it by clicking on image types in menus.
Keep loosing track of time? Try the clock widget in the 'more' menu. It even has hour and minute sounds.
Want to test something? try the 'tests' menu accessible from the help index.
Need Help? Try the help menu! Just click the 'help' button.
Did you know Zoxenpher can be configured to open Web URLs in your web browser? Check 'configuration help' to learn more!
Hold shift and leftclick a link to open it in a new bookmark dialog.
Want to skim through a page? Use shift+mouse wheel or PageUp/PageDown to scroll faster!
Quickly toggle image previews in a menu via Ctrl+i.